{"tid":564453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"懲教署二級懲教助理今起全年招聘！","createTime":"2018-02-18T04:12:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T11:39:06.000Z","uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"daa9b57f707a33be0fe31f754ef343698650a658","tid":564453,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T04:12:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1156228/xlarge/a24ce3c300686162d528e67562b433b0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1156228%2Fxlarge%2Fa24ce3c300686162d528e67562b433b0.jpg&h=ed50bd0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因應懲教署近年面對人手短缺和流失等問題，懲教署指，將由本年2月19日起全年招聘二級懲教助理，預計2018/19年度會聘不少於350人，而明日開始亦並會開展新一輪懲教主任招聘。署方指，以往考生在體能測試中只有60%人合格，特別在仰臥起坐一環姿勢不符，呼籲考生多練習和留意部門的資訊。<br />\n<br />\n懲教署職員訓練院院長楊賢妙指，署方近年自然流失率高，在2018/19年度將有逾200名懲教人員退休，為填補空缺決定全年招聘二級懲教助理，今年目標是招聘不少於350人，並由下月19日開展。另外，署方由明日起會公開招聘不少於50名懲教主任，至2月8日截止。<br />\n<br />\n投考懲教人員者，第一關是按受體能測試，包括仰臥起坐、90米穿梭跑、俯撐取放、800米跑、立地向上直跳等，但近年合格率只有約60%。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>考生在仰臥起坐急追次數　致姿勢不合格</strong><br />\n<br />\n懲教署職員訓練院體育組懲教主任譚敬文指，考生最常在仰臥起坐不合格，主因他們太急進去追求次數，忽略正確姿勢，如考生常拉衫借力致姿態不合格，提醒考生手指須要觸到鎖骨，向下時身體要觸到海棉。總懲教主任李英偉亦呼籲，考生準備面試前應多留意時事和部門資料，包括工作理念和發展方向等，並穿著合適服飾參加面試。<br />\n<br />\n二級懲教助理起薪點為每月19,220至20,365元；懲教主任起薪點則為每月33,320至41,955元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1156283/xlarge/3c5495bd7d3965b28ac3ee9efbd68fa7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1156283%2Fxlarge%2F3c5495bd7d3965b28ac3ee9efbd68fa7.jpg&h=02b8b9b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1156271/xlarge/ef60d8f84c3ed420ac974a0576537052.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1156271%2Fxlarge%2Fef60d8f84c3ed420ac974a0576537052.jpg&h=31939884&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1156280/xlarge/c596f9d65614bfa0f1a2140ba8a7111d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1156280%2Fxlarge%2Fc596f9d65614bfa0f1a2140ba8a7111d.jpg&h=90fc6900&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1156272/xlarge/421e38938b3e4fecd14cc46bbfaaae29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1156272%2Fxlarge%2F421e38938b3e4fecd14cc46bbfaaae29.jpg&h=01ea23b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1156275/xlarge/012f54b4dfb7f1786df7b147943c099f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1156275%2Fxlarge%2F012f54b4dfb7f1786df7b147943c099f.jpg&h=db963852&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1156277/xlarge/41314f3a92a38dbad1f555d4cdd5f776.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1156277%2Fxlarge%2F41314f3a92a38dbad1f555d4cdd5f776.jpg&h=ae3023fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1156274/xlarge/a5210bd10f2d7543602dbdf58e0cc5ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1156274%2Fxlarge%2Fa5210bd10f2d7543602dbdf58e0cc5ad.jpg&h=8fe50e49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1156284/xlarge/d4316111a9a90db1d79952ebe3559795.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1156284%2Fxlarge%2Fd4316111a9a90db1d79952ebe3559795.jpg&h=bc8d4ce8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1156276/xlarge/6ed23caf06f90756cdd0354c7be696c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1156276%2Fxlarge%2F6ed23caf06f90756cdd0354c7be696c0.jpg&h=f5a72798&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1156286/xlarge/b1c57317e9d91bec4cfe9096938fb206.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih